    "note": "Maps UI keys to Wikidata concepts + lexical categories. The build script (scripts/build-i18n.mjs) resolves them through Z33668 'word for concept' to a lemma per language. This is the ONLY source of chrome strings — including English. Keys with concept+category are attempted; keys with skip: true are not.",
    "authoritative": "This file is the single source of truth for what chrome zblocks translates and how. Changes here plus a rebuild propagate to every language.",
